snippet.title: COLLEGE BOWL ► Steam's Next Fest Trailer
snippet.description:
#COLLEGEBOWL

Play the Demo for COLLEGE BOWL on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1226160/College_Bowl/

College Bowl is a beautifully pixelated on-field simulation of American Football! Challenge college rivals on your way to winning a National title! Take on various game modes, including a deep Dynasty mode with in-depth recruiting, scouting, stat tracking, ranking, bowl games, yearly goals and more!
